ries went together. It just felt like the whole Tess story line could have been cut out of the book without any problems. It was all just really predictable, the second I read Rachel's chapter I knew where everything was going. Also that ending made me think of Jodi Picoult and her little twist endings and not in a good way. It just felt too coincidental for me to buy. So while I liked the complexity portrayed and the writing as well as the characters the plot just didn't do it for me at all.","rating":3,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/48650982?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2006595116"},"likeCount":155,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":11,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Work:kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.CoKCvRl7-p29krnpnmxBsQ":{"id":"kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.CoKCvRl7-p29krnpnmxBsQ","__typename":"Work","legacyId":23986788,"bestBook":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.FM-b5ID0Mh-6ynaGSLF-OQ"},"details":{"__typename":"WorkDetails","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/23986788-the-husband-s-secret","shelvesUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/shelves/23986788-the-husband-s-secret","publicationTime":1375167600000,"originalTitle":"The Husband's Secret ","awardsWon":[{"__typename":"Award","name":"Australian Book Industry Award (ABIA)","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/award/show/10795-australian-book-industry-award-abia","awardedAt":1388563200000,"category":"General Fiction","hasWon":false},{"__typename":"Award","name":"Goodreads Choice Award","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/award/show/21332-goodreads-choice-award","awardedAt":1357027200000,"category":"Fiction","hasWon":false}],"places":[{"__typename":"Places","name":"Sydney, New South Wales","countryName":"Australia","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/places/1030-sydney-new-south-wales","year":2012}],"characters":[{"__typename":"Charac